casebody.data:
Natalia KARNATCHEVA, et al., petitioners,
v.
JP MORGAN CHASE BANK, et al. No. 12-1303. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 704 F.3d 545 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied. Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
